description: From the manufacturer Key Features Extra Strong 50L Rubble Sacks Extra strong heavy duty rubble sacks for the toughest of jobs with leak resistance as standard. Our quality sacks and bags are suited for many different tasks including demanding use. Reusability with a Minimum Carbon Footprint in Mind Sustainable with traceability as we collect the waste within the UK, sort, process & recycle minimising our carbon footprint. Made in Britain with Quality (ISO 9001) & Environmental Management (ISO 14001) accredited compliance systems. True in Size & Capacity 580mm width & 760mm in length ensuring 50 Litre capacity for heavy loads. Our sacks and bags are made from quality grade re-used tear resistant 100% LDPE material which can be further recycled where facilities exist. Social Responsibility Supporting the invaluable worldwide work of Plasticbank. The aim of accelerating positive change in our business being more sustainable by making an impact against global poverty and pollution.
